Package com.camerontec.catalys.server.processor

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IEndOfDayPerformer  
    IExceptionListener
    Interface for objects that can process Exceptions.
    IFIXListener
    A FIX message processor that listens to messages from an external FIX session.
    IFIXMessageProcessor
    Interface for standard component for processing Catalys messages.
    IFIXSource
    A FIX message processor that is a source of messages destined to be sent to an external FIX session.
    IHasOptionalPartyRouting
    Interface which can be supported by ISelectors which can be associated with an IConnectionPoint which can optionally be used for message routing.
    IMessageProcessorEventTransformer
    This interface is used to define construction methods for message processor event messages.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FieldFilterByFixVersion
    For each message, this processor removes all fields that do not belong to the message type for a given FIX version.
    FIXListenerBase
    Base class for processors which listen for incoming FIX messages.
    FIXMessageProcessorBase
    Base class for all IFIXMessageProcessor classes.
    FIXSourceBase
    Base class for processors which are a source of FIX messages.
    FIXSourceListenerBase
    Base class for processors which process FIX messages in both directions.
    MessageListProcessor
    Utility class to send messages asynchronously (ie without waiting for the send to complete).
    MessageProcessorListEntry
    Holder for a processor and its associated ISelector objects (if any).
    NullMessageProcessor
    This the a null Message Processor.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    MessageProcessorRejectException
    Exception that can be thrown by an IFIXListener class which contains a FIX reject message.
    MessageProcessorResponseException
    Exception thrown by IFIXListeners when sending a FIX version specific response to a counterparty request.
    RoutingException
    Indicates that there was some problem routing data - eg FIX messages.
